<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="live-on">live on</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>继续活着；继续存在：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She died ten years ago but her memory lives on.
她十年前就去世了，但还留在人们的记忆中。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>以吃…为生；以…为主食；靠 (…钱) 生活：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We live on rice. 
我们以米饭为主食。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He lives on a salary of $500 a month. 
他靠每月500美元的薪水生活。</p></div></div>